{{Infobox dungeon |name = Victory Road Kalos |image = [[File:Victory Road Kalos.png|250px]] |caption = A map of Victory Road Kalos. |tokens = 750,500 |location = North of Routes 20 and 21, South of Pokémon League Kalos. }} '''Victory Road Kalos''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Kalos]]. It initially has 100 tiles arranged in a 10x10 square, including 10 chest tiles, 23 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile. Wild Encounters have 9,003,000 HP.
